entry.title: Samsung Galaxy Note Ultra Clear car case cell phone holder with 360° Rotation Ring Holder Kickstand
entry.summary:
Vendor: XpressTronics
Type: Cell Phone Cases
Price: 3.50

  • Compatible: Samsung Galaxy Note 20 Ultra only 
  • The phone case uses the soft edge of TPU to ensure that the phone will not be scratched when it is disassembled or installed, and the corners are reinforced to prevent falling.
  • The edge of the phone case will be slightly higher than the screen and lens (not obvious). When the phone is placed on the desktop, prevents friction between the screen and the desktop, causing scratches.
  • You can put the phone on the table at any angle with its 360-degree ring. At the same time, when you hold the phone with one hand, you can prevent the phone from slipping.
  • Different from other traditional ring phone cases, the phone case can place on the desktop levelly, at the same time, it is also very thin and light, it will not affect the feel of using the phone.
  • Slides easily in and out of pockets. Tactile buttons with precise cutouts raised lips to protect screen and camera. This Case allows you to experience your phone in a brand new way.
